query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.categoryId, c.name as category_name, c.slug
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.categoryId = c.id
WHERE c.slug LIKE '%zodiac%' OR c.slug LIKE '%生肖%'
LIMIT 20;
